  "None suggested yet": "Nog geen suggesties",
  "After the AI responds, a separate quiet API call generates the tracker JSON independently. Expect ~250–300s total per message (narrative + wait + tracker).": "Na het antwoord genereert een stille aanroep de JSON. ~250–300s/bericht.",
  "✓ Single API call — typically ~100–120s total": "✓ Eén API-aanroep — ~100–120s",
  "✓ No profile switching — eliminates message deletion risk": "✓ Geen profielwisseling — geen risico",
  "✓ AI has full narrative context for accurate tracking": "✓ AI heeft volledige context",
  "✓ 2–3× faster than Separate mode in practice": "✓ 2–3× sneller dan Gescheiden",
  "✗ Uses tokens from the main response budget (~1,700 tokens for tracker)": "✗ Gebruikt tokens van het hoofdbudget (~1.700)",
  "✗ May slightly reduce narrative length on token-limited models": "✗ Kan verhalenlengte iets verkorten",
  "✓ Clean responses — narrative never token-competes with tracker": "✓ Schone antwoorden — geen tokencompetitie",
  "✓ Dedicated token budget for tracker output": "✓ Toegewijd budget voor tracker",
  "✓ Can use a different connection profile/preset": "✓ Kan ander profiel/preset gebruiken",
  "✗ Two API calls per message — 2–3× slower than Together mode": "✗ Twee API-aanroepen — 2–3× langzamer",
  "✗ ~12s dead time between calls (chat save + preset switching)": "✗ ~12s wachttijd tussen aanroepen",
  "✗ Tracker prompt is ~10K+ tokens at 8 context msgs — reduce to 3–4 for speed": "✗ Prompt ~10K+ bij 8 berichten — verlaag naar 3–4",
  "✗ Profile switching can cause message deletion (race condition with other extensions)": "✗ Profielwisseling kan berichten verwijderen",
  "✗ Embeds previous snapshot into narrative call (~1.9K tokens) unless Embed snapshots = 0": "✗ Voegt vorige snapshot toe (~1.9K) tenzij = 0",
  "How many recent messages to include when generating tracker updates.": "Hoeveel recente berichten opnemen.",
  "Separate mode only — Together mode uses ST's full context automatically.": "Alleen Gescheiden — Samen gebruikt STs context.",
  "Fastest. Good for simple 1-on-1 scenes (~5K token prompt)": "Snelste. Voor 1-op-1 scènes (~5K)",
  "Balanced. Recommended for most scenes (~8–12K tokens)": "Gebalanceerd. Voor de meeste (~8–12K)",
  "Better continuity for complex multi-character scenes (~12–20K tokens)": "Betere continuïteit voor complexe scènes (~12–20K)",
  "Maximum context but significantly slower and more expensive": "Maximale context maar langzamer en duurder",
  "This is the biggest factor in Separate mode speed. At 8 msgs your tracker prompt is ~10K tokens — doubling roughly doubles generation time. Lower values (3–4) can cut tracker time by 40–60%.": "Grootste factor. Bij 8 berichten ~10K — verdubbelen verdubbelt de tijd. 3–4 vermindert 40–60%.",
  "Separate mode only.": "Alleen Gescheiden modus.",
  "How many times to retry if the tracker API call returns invalid JSON.": "Hoe vaak opnieuw proberen bij ongeldige JSON.",
  "Built-in preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Optimized for structured JSON output on GLM-5.": "Preset: temp=0.6, top_p=0.95, freq_pen=0.15, max_tokens=4096. Voor JSON op GLM-5.",
  "Embed recent scene snapshots into the narrative conversation context so the AI can reference tracker state while writing. Only applies in Separate mode. The tracker's own API call always receives the previous snapshot regardless of this setting.": "Bedt snapshots in de context in. Alleen Gescheiden. Tracker ontvangt altijd de vorige.",
  "Each embedded snapshot adds ~1.9K tokens to your narrative prompt. Set to 0 to eliminate this overhead — the tracker API call still receives previous state independently. Set to 1 for narrative continuity (AI remembers scene details). Values above 1 are rarely beneficial.": "Elke snapshot +~1.9K. 0 om te elimineren. 1 voor continuïteit. Boven 1 zelden nuttig.",
  "Injected as invisible context — AI treats it as authoritative background info. Best for continuity without polluting the conversation.": "Als onzichtbare context — gezaghebbende achtergrondinfo.",
  "Appears as if the user said it — some models respond more attentively.": "Verschijnt alsof de gebruiker het zei — sommige modellen reageren beter.",
  "Appears as previous AI output — can reinforce the AI's own memory but may confuse some models.": "Als eerdere AI-output — kan geheugen versterken maar verwarren.",
